    dc:date "2014" ;
    dc:title "Nematodes from galls on Myrtaceae. VIII. Fergusobia from small galls on shoot buds, with descriptions of four new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.286991>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.286992> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.286991>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Habitus drawings of Fergusobia spp. (most undescribed) collected from small shoot bud galls: A, MSp 40 from LPG on E. marginata; B, F. rileyi from LPG on Corymbia sp.; C, MSp 61 from LPG on E. delegatensis; D, MSp 55 from LPG on E. amygdalina; E, MSp 78 from petiole PG on E. blakelyi; F, MSp 59 from LPG on E. obliqua; G, MSp 41 from LPG on E. pauciflora; H, MSp 30 from LPG on E. tereticornis; I, F. gomphocephalae n. sp. from unilocular stem and bud galls on E. gomphocephala; J, F. leucoxylonaeae n. sp. from multilocular shoot bud galls on E. leucoxylon; K, F. sporangae n. sp. from UABG on E. leucoxylon; L, MSp 21 from UABG on E. microcarpa; M, Fergusobia sp. from UABG on E. odorata; N, MSp 80 from UABG on E. viminalis; O, MSp 79 from multilocular shoot bud gall on E. fasciculosa; P, MSp 47 from AUBG on E. cladocalyx; Q, MSp 77 from multilocular shoot bud gall on E. confluens; R, MSp 39 from UABG form 2 on E. viminalis; S, F. schmidti n. sp. from multilocular conoid axial shoot bud gall on E. camaldulensis. Scale bars = 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/286991/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.286992>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Spicules from Fergusobia spp. collected from small shoot bud galls: A, MSp 40 from E. marginata; B, F. rileyi; C, MSp 61 from E. delegatensis; D, MSp 55 from E. amygdalina; E, MSp 78 from E. blakelyi; F, MSp 59 from E. obliqua; G, MSp 41 from E. pauciflora; H, Fergusobia sp. from ABG from Eucalyptus sp. at Brisbane, QLD; I, MSp 30 from E. tereticornis; J, F. gomphocephalae n. sp.; K, F. leucoxylonae n. sp.; L, F. sporangae n. sp.; M, MSp 21 from E. microcarpae; N, Fergusobia sp. from E. odorata; O, MSp 28 from E.? siderophloia; P, MSp 39 from E. viminalis UABG form 2; Q, MSp 79 from E. fasciculosae; R, MSp 47 from E. cladocalyx; S, MSp 77 from E. confluens; T, Fergusobia sp. from LPG from Eucalyptus sp. at Indooroopilly, Brisbane, QLD; U, F. schmidti n. sp. Not drawn to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/286992/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

